        "text": "Online, however, the vast majority of businesses are virtuous by taking advantage of less vigilant consumer behaviour (partial reading of contract terms, superficial reading of information) to engage in misleading commercial practices. They can develop deceptive or addictive interface designs and functionalities, personalised practices targeting minors, older people, people with mental impairments or who may cause risky behaviours, processes that complicate the cancellation and renewal of digital subscriptions, or unfair contractual clauses with forced acceptance.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s6",
          "section_path": [
