        "text": "These practices directly harm businesses that comply with European standards, investing in their compliance, and thus their brands and products. By not sanctioning these practices, the European market creates a structural distortion of competition. Virtuous businesses are penalised because they are not able to compete on an equal footing with those circumventing European standards.",
